        {
            "name": "Exporta\u00e7\u00e3o de Segmentos",
            "description": "\nEndpoints para exporta\u00e7\u00e3o de clientes de um segmento para Excel\/CSV.\n\nA exporta\u00e7\u00e3o de segmentos permite extrair a lista de clientes de um segmento espec\u00edfico\nem formatos Excel (XLSX) ou CSV. Existem duas abordagens dispon\u00edveis:\n\n- **Exporta\u00e7\u00e3o Ass\u00edncrona**: Recomendada para segmentos grandes (mais de 50.000 clientes).\n  Um job \u00e9 disparado em background e voc\u00ea pode acompanhar o progresso.\n- **Exporta\u00e7\u00e3o S\u00edncrona (Streaming)**: Para segmentos menores, oferece download imediato.\n\n<aside class=\"notice\">\nTodos os endpoints de exporta\u00e7\u00e3o requerem autentica\u00e7\u00e3o via Sanctum.\n<\/aside>",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Listar colunas dispon\u00edveis",
                    "request": {
                        "url": {
                            "host": "{{baseUrl}}",
                            "path": "api\/v1\/segments\/export\/columns",
                            "query": [],
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}\/api\/v1\/segments\/export\/columns"
                        },
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application\/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application\/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": null,
                        "description": "Retorna a lista de todas as colunas dispon\u00edveis para exporta\u00e7\u00e3o e as colunas padr\u00e3o.\nUse este endpoint para construir interfaces de sele\u00e7\u00e3o de colunas na exporta\u00e7\u00e3o.\n\n**Colunas dispon\u00edveis:**\n- `id` - ID interno do cliente\n- `external_id` - ID externo do cliente (da plataforma de origem)\n- `email` - E-mail do cliente\n- `phone` - Telefone do cliente\n- `first_name` - Primeiro nome\n- `last_name` - Sobrenome\n- `birth_date` - Data de nascimento\n- `total_orders_count` - Total de pedidos realizados\n- `lifetime_value` - Valor total gasto pelo cliente (LTV)\n- `average_ticket` - Ticket m\u00e9dio\n- `last_purchase_at` - Data da \u00faltima compra\n- `lifecycle_stage` - Est\u00e1gio do ciclo de vida (new, active, at_risk, lost, vip)\n- `created_at` - Data de cria\u00e7\u00e3o do registro\n- `updated_at` - Data da \u00faltima atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o"
                    },
                    "response": [
                        {
                            "header": [],
                            "code": 200,
                            "body": "{\n  \"available_columns\": [\"id\", \"external_id\", \"email\", \"phone\", \"first_name\", \"last_name\", \"birth_date\", \"total_orders_count\", \"lifetime_value\", \"average_ticket\", \"last_purchase_at\", \"lifecycle_stage\", \"created_at\", \"updated_at\"],\n  \"default_columns\": [\"email\", \"first_name\", \"last_name\", \"phone\", \"total_orders_count\", \"lifetime_value\", \"average_ticket\", \"last_purchase_at\"]\n}",
                            "name": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "header": [],
                            "code": 401,
                            "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Unauthenticated.\"\n}",
                            "name": "N\u00e3o autenticado"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "name": "Iniciar exporta\u00e7\u00e3o ass\u00edncrona",
                    "request": {
                        "url": {
                            "host": "{{baseUrl}}",
                            "path": "api\/v1\/segments\/:segment_id\/export",
                            "query": [
                                {
                                    "key": "columns",
                                    "value": "email%2Cfirst_name%2Clast_name%2Cphone%2Clifetime_value",
                                    "description": "Colunas para exportar, separadas por v\u00edrgula. Se n\u00e3o informado, usa as colunas padr\u00e3o. Colunas dispon\u00edveis: id, external_id, email, phone, first_name, last_name, birth_date, total_orders_count, lifetime_value, average_ticket, last_purchase_at, lifecycle_stage, created_at, updated_at.",
                                    "disabled": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "format",
                                    "value": "xlsx",
                                    "description": "Formato do arquivo de sa\u00edda. Valores aceitos: xlsx, csv. Default: xlsx.",
                                    "disabled": false
                                }
                            ],
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}\/api\/v1\/segments\/:segment_id\/export?columns=email%2Cfirst_name%2Clast_name%2Cphone%2Clifetime_value&format=xlsx",
                            "variable": [
                                {
                                    "id": "segment_id",
                                    "key": "segment_id",
                                    "value": "1",
                                    "description": "The ID of the segment."
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "segment",
                                    "key": "segment",
                                    "value": "1",
                                    "description": "ID do segmento a ser exportado."
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application\/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application\/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": null,
                        "description": "Inicia um job em background para exportar os clientes do segmento.\nRecomendado para segmentos com mais de 50.000 clientes.\n\nO processo funciona da seguinte forma:\n1. Esta requisi\u00e7\u00e3o dispara um job em background\n2. Use o endpoint de status para verificar quando a exporta\u00e7\u00e3o terminou\n3. Fa\u00e7a o download do arquivo quando o status for \"completed\""
                    },
                    "response": [
                        {
