                                    "description": "Colunas para exportar, separadas por v\u00edrgula. Se n\u00e3o informado, usa as colunas padr\u00e3o (email, first_name, last_name, phone, total_orders_count, lifetime_value, average_ticket, last_purchase_at).",
                                    "disabled": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "format",
                                    "value": "csv",
